[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0852","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0852.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1006","title":"Groupwise 企业级邮件系统 Web 服务器 GWWEB.EXE 路径遍历漏洞","description":"Groupwise 企业级邮件系统 Web 服务器 GWWEB.EXE 存在路径遍历漏洞，攻击者可远程访问 HELP 参数获取服务器的内部路径结构，并读取位于 Web 根目录之外的 .htm 文件。该漏洞源于应用程序泄露绝对文件系统路径信息，缺乏对 HELP 异步的充分访问控制。攻击者可通过构造恶意请求枚举服务器目录结构，进而访问服务器之外的敏感文件。该漏洞已在 GroupWise 5.2 和 5.5 版本中被证实，影响范围涵盖该邮件系统的 Web 界面帮助功能。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1006"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.503","remediation":"建议升级 Novell GroupWise 到已修复该路径遍历问题的官方版本（GroupWise 5.5 EP 及以上），并应用 Novell 发布的对应 Support Pack 补丁。如无法立即升级，可在 Web 服务器前端部署反向代理或 WAF 规则过滤 HELP 参数中的 \"../\"、绝对路径等遍历字符，并禁用或限制 GWWEB.EXE 对敏感目录的访问，仅开放必要虚拟路径作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94571433731824&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8f7915616bad1c7280e28216588ab0258074928/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1006.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1006","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1006.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ea13d8ca97b52327fe351b64da51866911834231/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1006.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/424512debdca84cc53ffa1fb3810a74f7b1905a5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j6r8-2wq6-f58q/GHSA-j6r8-2wq6-f58q.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/groupwise_web_interface_help_hole.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1006.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000946.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--66e530a7-b849-4eeb-881d-b8c411c494b7.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0852.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0850","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0850.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1005","title":"Novell GroupWise 5.2/5.5 GWWEB.EXE 目录遍历与路径泄露漏洞","description":"Novell GroupWise 5.2 和 5.5 版本的 Web 接口组件 GWWEB.EXE 存在两个安全缺陷。首先，HELP 参数会向客户端返回服务器完整文件系统路径，泄露敏感的内部目录结构信息。其次，攻击者通过在 HELP 参数中注入 '../' 目录遍历序列，可绕过访问控制读取服务器上任意位置的 .htm 文件或浏览目录内容。此外，向 GWWEB.EXE 发送超长字符串可触发 GWINTER.NLM 的缓冲区溢出，导致服务崩溃。攻击者无需身份认证，仅需向目标服务器发送构造的 HTTP 请求即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1005"],"sources":["cve","bugtraq","exploit-db"],"published":"1999-12-19","updated":"2026-07-19","remediation":"升级至 Novell GroupWise 5.5 后续支持包或更高版本，修复 GWWEB.EXE 的目录遍历与缓冲区溢出缺陷。若无法立即升级，应在 Netscape Enterprise Server 或前端代理中配置 URL 过滤规则，拦截 HELP 参数中包含 '../' 或 '..' 的请求，并将 GWWEB.EXE 进程权限限制在其 Web 根目录范围内，禁止越权访问其他文件系统路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94571433731824&w=2","http://www.osvdb.org/3413","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/879","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19682"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19682"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0850.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0850.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0850.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1680","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1680.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0995","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Local Security Authority 子系统 LsaLookupSids 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 的本地安全权威子系统（LSA）在处理 LsaLookupSids 函数调用时存在输入验证缺陷（CWE-20）。该函数用于根据安全标识符（SID）查找对应的账户信息，但远程攻击者可通过构造畸形、格式不正确的 SID 参数发起请求。由于 LSA 未对传入参数进行充分校验，接收到畸形 SID 后会导致 Local Security Authority Subsystem Service 进程异常崩溃，进而引发目标系统拒绝服务，需重启才能恢复。该漏洞影响运行 Windows NT 4.0 的远程主机，攻击者可未经身份认证通过网络远程触发，无需本地登录权限或用户交互，利用方式即向目标发送包含畸形 SID 参数的 LsaLookupSids 请求。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0995"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.080","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 发布的安全补丁 KB248185，该修复已包含在 MS99-056（Syskey Keystream Reuse）公告的补丁包中。受影响系统包括 Windows NT Workstation 4.0、Windows NT Server 4.0、Windows NT Server 4.0 Enterprise Edition 以及 Windows NT Server 4.0 Terminal Server Edition。已应用 MS99-056 补丁的用户无需额外操作。如短期内无法安装补丁，可在边界防火墙上封锁 NetBIOS 及 TCP 445 端口的访问，以阻断远程攻击者向 LSA 发送畸形 SID 请求的路径。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，长期缓解措施为将系统升级至受支持的 Windows 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ248185","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/875","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-057","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-0995.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/bf63c766a0e51c24a528a42a3e26e4fdf58db9e8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0995.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0995","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/08f8d33c39c79a3a93a8b5c441facde3f9e3cc7d/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0995.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0995.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f43f79d7ee652229af6058b1c98133bb5bbc17fb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m7p3-89hq-9rch/GHSA-m7p3-89hq-9rch.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--fce51a26-ebf8-401d-911b-712877e4db93.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1680.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0837","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0837.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1001","title":"思科 缓存引擎 基于NULL凭证的认证绕过漏洞","description":"思科缓存引擎（Cisco Cache Engine）在处理用户访问认证时存在访问验证缺陷，未对登录凭据进行严格校验。远程攻击者可在认证请求中提交空的用户名与密码（null username and password），绕过正常的身份验证机制，从而未经授权访问受保护的缓存服务或管理功能。该漏洞影响运行相关版本软件的思科缓存引擎设备，攻击无需本地权限，仅需网络可达并能够发起认证请求即可利用，危害程度中等，可能导致缓存内容被非法访问或设备配置被未授权操作。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1001"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.860","remediation":"将 Cisco Cache Engine 升级至修复该空凭证认证绕过问题的官方固件版本（具体版本号以 Cisco 安全公告为准），并在无法立即升级时，于边界防火墙或访问控制列表（ACL）上限制仅允许受信任管理网段访问设备的管理端口，同时禁用匿名/空用户名空密码登录并强制配置强口令认证。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-1001","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-1001.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/786262dea273b0bddfc7eb6f6950f11b9f01c05c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1001.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1001","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/165075bb4c3675993ac058501ff8575bd07a9ca0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1001.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1001.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f43f79d7ee652229af6058b1c98133bb5bbc17fb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jw6g-mwcg-w65v/GHSA-jw6g-mwcg-w65v.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1001.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87020/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/lgp171188/launchpad/blob/eafda459366f2c43246e9c4fa98b8c008434bb68/lib/lp/bugs/scripts/cveimport.py"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0837.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0837.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0833","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0833.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1000","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9116,\"outputTokens\":17,\"totalTokens\":10797}}","description":"Cisco Cache Engine 的 Web 管理界面存在信息泄露漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可直接访问管理界面的性能统计页面，无需认证即可查看设备的性能统计信息，包括缓存命中率、流量统计、系统资源使用等敏感运行数据。该漏洞影响 Cisco Cache Engine 多个版本，攻击者仅需通过网络访问管理界面的特定 URL 路径即可获取敏感性能数据，无需任何身份认证或特殊权限。攻击者可利用泄露的性能统计信息分析设备负载情况、网络流量模式及系统配置，为后续攻击提供情报支持。Cisco 已发布补丁修复该漏洞，建议升级到修复版本并限制管理界面的网络访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1000"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.750","remediation":"建议升级 Cisco Cache Engine 至厂商修复后的软件版本（如 ACNS 4.x 或更高版本）。同时应对 Web 管理界面配置访问控制列表（ACL），仅允许受信任的管理网段访问；关闭或限制未授权用户对性能统计页面的访问，并为管理界面启用强身份认证。如无法立即升级，可在边界防火墙上限制对 Cache Engine 管理端口（如 TCP 8001/8888）的外部访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-1000","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-1000.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/786262dea273b0bddfc7eb6f6950f11b9f01c05c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1000.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1000","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/165075bb4c3675993ac058501ff8575bd07a9ca0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1000.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1000.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f43f79d7ee652229af6058b1c98133bb5bbc17fb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6xm7-wpgr-j445/GHSA-6xm7-wpgr-j445.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1000.json","https://github.com/GiovanniMenon/llm4cve/blob/3ca85b2ae823c06810c546f320c2cd2f2707043f/README.md","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--82f3f412-fe84-463c-a838-96c287166f4d.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0833.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0833.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0830","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0830.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0998","title":"思科 缓存引擎 缓存内容替换漏洞","description":"思科（Cisco）Cache Engine 缓存引擎存在安全漏洞，攻击者能够向缓存引擎发送特制的请求，将缓存中已存储的合法 Web 内容替换为攻击者控制的恶意内容。该漏洞影响部署了 Cisco Cache Engine 并对用户 Web 访问进行内容缓存的网络环境，攻击者可借此实施内容篡改、钓鱼或投毒等中间人式攻击。利用该漏洞无需身份认证，攻击者只需能够与目标缓存引擎进行网络通信，即可注入伪造的缓存响应，使后续访问该内容的用户获取被篡改的数据。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0998"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.483","remediation":"建议将 Cisco Cache Engine 升级至修复该漏洞的官方固件版本（具体版本号参见 Cisco 安全公告），并及时应用 Cisco 发布的相关软件更新。如暂无法升级，可在上游边界设备配置访问控制列表（ACL）仅允许受信任源站回源，禁止未经授权的外部主机向缓存引擎推送或替换内容，同时在缓存引擎上启用内容完整性校验与来源认证，限制管理接口仅对内部网络开放，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0998","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-0998.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/bf63c766a0e51c24a528a42a3e26e4fdf58db9e8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0998.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0998","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/08f8d33c39c79a3a93a8b5c441facde3f9e3cc7d/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0998.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0998.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f43f79d7ee652229af6058b1c98133bb5bbc17fb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cp4f-jgpj-pg53/GHSA-cp4f-jgpj-pg53.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0998.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87024/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0830.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0826","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0826.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0994","title":"Microsoft Windows NT SYSKEY 密钥流重用导致密码破解漏洞","description":"Windows NT 在启用 SYSKEY 功能后，对 SAM 数据库中的密码哈希进行加密时错误地重用了同一密钥流（keystream），而非为每个加密操作生成独立的随机密钥流。攻击者若能够访问存储在磁盘或内存中的加密 SAM 密码哈希，可利用已知明文攻击手段还原出加密所用的密钥流并据此破解用户密码，进而获取系统账号权限。该漏洞影响启用 SYSKEY 的 Windows NT 系统，攻击前提是需要本地或远程（如通过备份文件、注册表导出）获取到加密后的 SAM 数据库，属于本地信息泄露与密码破解类风险，CVSS 评分约为 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0994"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:28.960","remediation":"建议立即更新到 Windows Server 2003 SP1 或更高版本以获得完整的修复，或升级到 Windows XP Pro with SP2，这些版本修正了 SYSKEY 密钥流重用漏洞。如无法立即更新 Windows，可禁用 SYSKEY 功能并同时在域控制器上启用强制密码加密，短期内可以通过网络策略禁止明文密码存储并强制实施复杂密码策略来降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ248183","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/873","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-056","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-0994.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d69ab21f83909859ed75ab8ba3287f9f633b856f/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0994.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0994","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/08f8d33c39c79a3a93a8b5c441facde3f9e3cc7d/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0994.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0994.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f43f79d7ee652229af6058b1c98133bb5bbc17fb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r7rj-gr4g-8x94/GHSA-r7rj-gr4g-8x94.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0994.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0826.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1681","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1681.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0996","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16349,\"outputTokens\":50,\"totalTokens\":16399}}","description":"Infoseek Ultraseek 2.1 及 3.1 版本（运行于 Windows NT 平台）的搜索引擎存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该漏洞源于程序在处理用户发起的 HTTP GET 请求时，未对请求长度进行边界校验，攻击者可通过构造超长的 GET 请求数据触发缓冲区溢出。未经身份认证的远程攻击者只需向目标服务器发送特制长请求，即可覆盖内存并远程执行任意命令。受影响的版本为 Ultraseek 2.1 与 3.1 for NT，攻击无需本地权限或用户交互，危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0996"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.210","remediation":"升级到 Infoseek Ultraseek 2.1/3.1 for NT 的最新官方补丁版本，若无最新补丁可禁用 Ultraseek 服务或使用所有到来的入站流量进行网络层过滤以阻止攻击媒介，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.eeye.com/html/Research/Advisories/AD19991215.html","http://www.osvdb.org/6490","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19679","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/bf63c766a0e51c24a528a42a3e26e4fdf58db9e8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0996.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0996","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-0996.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/08f8d33c39c79a3a93a8b5c441facde3f9e3cc7d/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0996.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f43f79d7ee652229af6058b1c98133bb5bbc17fb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j7c5-2gh9-m7cm/GHSA-j7c5-2gh9-m7cm.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/LubyRuffy/plugins/blob/f873b19f27c95eaf2993ca4acde5cb7965d2ee3f/pre2008/ultraseek_detect.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0996.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000940.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1681.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1314","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1314.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0935","title":"Greg Matthews Classifieds.cgi 1.0 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Classifieds.cgi 1.0 存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 CGI 表单中的隐藏变量提交恶意系统命令，导致任意命令执行。该漏洞源于程序未对用户输入进行有效过滤，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，可完全控制目标服务器。影响运行 Classifieds.cgi 1.0 的 Web 服务器，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0935"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:21.687","remediation":"该漏洞源于 classifieds.cgi 1.0 未对表单隐藏变量做任何过滤，导致远程攻击者可通过构造恶意 HTTP 请求直接执行任意系统命令。由于该 CGI 脚本已停止维护超过 20 年，建议立即从服务器上删除或替换 classifieds.cgi，改用支持参数化输入验证的现代 Web 应用（如采用 PHP/Python 框架重写），并在 Web 服务器层禁用 CGI 执行权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0935","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20442","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/aa3114da1227373bef7855dba21bcaa5f0e0ad76/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0935.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0935","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/8854c056beab250ba690e2bcc8887feb4c1f8139/1999/CVE-1999-0935/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-0935.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/b4ddb28f94d250449ab64c1617f45b1f91701fa2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0935.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xfgf-763r-q2wj/GHSA-xfgf-763r-q2wj.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/dangerous_cgis.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--272aaefe-4657-4097-86f2-5fd2b7ea3059.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1314.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1314.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1314.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0858","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0858.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1010","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9117,\"outputTokens\":19,\"totalTokens\":10800}}","description":"OpenSSH 1.2.27 版本的 SSH 服务端在密钥协商阶段存在安全策略绕过缺陷。按照服务端安全策略本应禁止客户端使用\"none\"加密算法（即不加密的明文传输），但受影响的服务器在协商过程中未能正确校验客户端所选加密方式，导致客户端可以强制使用\"none\"密码套件建立连接。攻击条件为攻击者能够与目标 OpenSSH 1.2.27 服务建立 SSH 连接，并在密钥交换阶段协商加密算法。成功利用后，攻击者与该服务的通信将不经过任何加密保护，导致会话内容以明文方式传输，从而可被中间人监听、窃取凭据或篡改数据，造成机密性破坏。该漏洞影响运行 OpenSSH 1.2.27 的服务器，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级较低，但可能削弱 SSH 通信的安全性保障。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1010"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.990","remediation":"升级 OpenSSH 至 1.2.28 或更高版本（修复了允许客户端使用 \"none\" 加密算法的策略绕过问题）。若无法立即升级，可在服务端配置文件 sshd_config 中设置 Ciphers 明确限定为已批准的加密算法列表，禁止使用 \"none\"，并重启 sshd 服务生效。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94519142415338&w=2","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-1010.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/9a9b6476a3f4a52ffa21ec6ed80d737eb0fc242b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1010.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1010","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1010.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1010.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/424512debdca84cc53ffa1fb3810a74f7b1905a5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wwmx-q2rq-7qgv/GHSA-wwmx-q2rq-7qgv.json","https://github.com/phx/cvescan/blob/d8d463e490d1d2d785179e8ace7ff59c2ea15f1f/README.md","https://github.com/privy-cafe/DollarLinuxClub/blob/57ae5d72b23dd6fe9fc5fca4dd120ffdf9dca123/misc/efnetretards.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/6ace77d8f88177c3c838b9b8d872bf7a08773429/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-10xx/CVE-1999-1010.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--0d650879-12f5-4812-85c1-eb23e0c89acc.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0858.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1668","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1668.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0993","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9110,\"outputTokens\":23,\"totalTokens\":10797}}","description":"标签之间。<value>Microsoft Exchange 5.5 存在访问控制列表（ACL）处理漏洞，对 ACL 的修改不会立即生效，需要等待目录存储缓存刷新后才能生效。未经身份验证的远程攻击者可以利用此漏洞，在 ACL 修改后、缓存刷新前的时间窗口内，使用已被撤销的权限访问 Exchange 服务器资源，导致未授权访问敏感信息或执行未授权操作。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Exchange 5.5 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级较高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0993"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-13T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:28.833","remediation":"建议将 Microsoft Exchange 5.5 升级至 Service Pack 4，并安装最新累积补丁以修复 ACL 缓存刷新缺陷。作为临时缓解措施，修改访问控制列表后应立即手动刷新目录存储缓存（重启 Directory Store 服务或使用管理工具强制刷新），确保权限变更即时生效，避免旧缓存导致越权访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0993","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-0993.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d69ab21f83909859ed75ab8ba3287f9f633b856f/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0993.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0993","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c9ec7f26a52f816468b636e23146049097db5070/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0993.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0993.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f43f79d7ee652229af6058b1c98133bb5bbc17fb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r287-63xg-jpw7/GHSA-r287-63xg-jpw7.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0993.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88086/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1668.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0842","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0842.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1003","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1728,\"inputTokens\":9065,\"outputTokens\":23,\"totalTokens\":10816}}","description":"Jgaa 开发的 WarFTPd 1.70 是一款运行于 Windows 平台的 FTP 守护进程。该版本在处理客户端连接时存在资源管理缺陷，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可向目标服务器大量、快速地发起 TCP 连接请求（连接洪水/Connection Flooding），耗尽服务器端的连接资源与系统处理能力，导致服务无法响应正常请求，最终造成拒绝服务（DoS）。攻击仅需网络可达目标 21 端口并能够建立大量连接即可实施，无需任何凭据或特殊权限，影响运行 WarFTPd 1.70 的服务器可用性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1003"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-13T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.130","remediation":"强烈建议将 War FTP Daemon 1.70 迁移至当前受支持的 FTP 服务器，如 vsftpd 3.0.5 或 ProFTPD 1.3.8 及以上版本，这些版本已内置连接速率限制与并发控制机制。如短期内无法替换，应在防火墙或 iptables 层对 21 端口启用连接速率限制，例如使用 hashlimit 模块限制同一源 IP 每秒新建连接不超过 5 次，并在系统内核参数中调低 tcp_synack_retries 与 tcp_syncookies 阈值以减缓 SYN 洪水冲击。同时建议部署 fail2ban 监控 FTP 异常连接行为，自动封禁高频访问源 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-1003","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/786262dea273b0bddfc7eb6f6950f11b9f01c05c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1003.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1003","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1003.md","https://github.com/diannaofengzi/POC/blob/14d504f7488db9229f6f02be54aab53e3cfee0dc/databases/1999/database/CVE-1999-1003/README.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/165075bb4c367599