57","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0857.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1009","title":"Disney Go Express Search 远程未授权访问和信息篡改漏洞","description":"Disney Go Express Search 存在信息泄露与篡改漏洞，其原理在于该软件会在用户系统上启动一个本地 HTTP 服务，且未对访问进行有效的身份认证与权限控制。远程攻击者无需任何凭证，只需连接到运行在用户系统上的该 HTTP 服务，即可读取并修改用户的搜索信息，从而破坏用户搜索数据的机密性与完整性。攻击条件较低，仅需目标用户运行了存在缺陷的 Disney Go Express Search 且服务端口可被远程访问。该漏洞主要影响运行该软件的个人用户系统，CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级为低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1009"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.870","remediation":"将 Disney Go Express Search 升级至最新官方版本，或通过修改系统注册表永久禁用该软件的 Go Express Search 功能，并在网络层配置访问控制列表限制对相关端口的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-1009","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/9a9b6476a3f4a52ffa21ec6ed80d737eb0fc242b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1009.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1009","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1009.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a6f1dc1488b4a75cccf07339e6a0f0ab45fc38ad/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1009.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/424512debdca84cc53ffa1fb3810a74f7b1905a5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gg88-hgcr-39f4/GHSA-gg88-hgcr-39f4.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1009.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000932.txt","https://github.com/masterfabric/masterfabric-pre-release/blob/d9d6f5c519248b656db787087e36b71c4b7a8ee9/cases/reports/nextjs_security_report.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1009.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0857.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0857.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0020","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0020.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0289","title":"Apache HTTP Server Win32 附加点号致信息泄露漏洞","description":"Apache Web Server for Win32 存在文件访问控制绕过漏洞。当攻击者在请求 URL 末尾附加一个点号（.）时，服务器可能绕过正常权限检查，导致受限制文件被未授权访问。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用此漏洞读取目标系统中的敏感文件（如配置文件、密码文件等），造成信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Apache for Win32 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0289"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:04.840","remediation":"升级到 Apache 1.3.12 或更高版本，该漏洞已在 1.3.x 后续版本中修复。如无法升级，在 Apache 配置中使用 `RewriteRule` 或 `AliasMatch` 拒绝所有以 `.` 结尾的 URL 请求，或在 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）层面过滤 URL 末尾的 `.` 字符作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0289","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0289.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0289","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0289.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0289.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0289.json","https://github.com/openbmc/openbmc/blob/798e84e356727c60a18eb3d0b86fb61b9862fb74/upstream-layers/meta-openembedded/meta-webserver/recipes-httpd/apache2/apache2_2.4.68.bb","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4